          "reviewBody": "Trust me, there are better ICSE schools at Barrackpore. Teaching staff used to be good at the time Zaki sir was present. After his demise, they started hiring teachers without a proper interview, as a result of which, students could not process their teachings properly. Management is horrible. Bathrooms are unhygienic. Classrooms don't have proper ventilation and fans. Would not recommend",
